.DS_Store

# Vite GUI bundle — regenerated by `mvn package` (frontend-maven-plugin →
# `npm run build` → vite outDir = src/main/resources/static). Treating it as
# a build artifact keeps diffs sane and prevents stale bundles from drifting
# from source. A fresh clone needs `mvn package` (or at least `cd ui && npm
# install && npm run build`) before `java -jar` will serve the GUI.
fhir-proxy/src/main/resources/static/
